<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 14 at 10:31AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Snow will cause travel difficulties through late this
evening...
Periods of snow will cause minor travel difficulties through this
evening. 1 to 3 inches accumulation are expected, with highest
accumulations over north-facing slopes and foothills. Snow is
expected to gradually diminish late this evening.</description>
